Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下船 讓我下船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來了 就要出來了 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我振作些 濃眉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱暈船了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的大浪確實扛不住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.61,0:00:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…讓船不要搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暈船而已嘛 真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.68,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此 但這樣晃真扛不住啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先找個地方休息 等天氣好轉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和預定的航線有些偏離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但東邊應該有座小島
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.88,0:00:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一說我倒想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中立海域的無人島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.14,0:01:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…對 是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.66,0:01:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去這兒吧 去避避…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了 趕緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉舵 向東北方航向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是鳴人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪確實很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當厲害啊 大家都要吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓凱老師稍事休息 所以才來這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們又執行什麼任務呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是根據綱手大人的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去東海？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.26,0:03:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四次忍界大戰很快就要開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要準備充足的秘藥以及兵糧丸的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七草島 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是藥草的寶庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地圖上標有藥草所在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.25,0:04:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼陀羅草 活力人參 紅蠑螈 大蔓籐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是什麼都有呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有餘力去看看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切不可勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小櫻就成了隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱老師睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬事準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時隨地可以出發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了鹿丸的十班殘餘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是殘餘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是多餘的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們七班不也是少了鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是各做各的去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐井應該也去執行其他任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都有自己的任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不用做沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來有很重大的任務等著鳴人去完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次出航也是為了這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也要等凱老師恢復後才能出航
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如幫幫我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採藥草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是 采草而已 游刃有餘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 都多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在看什麼呢 完全不對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全摸不清頭腦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不如和他們兩人一起照看凱老師的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想等凱先生恢復後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商討一下航海日程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 留下也沒啥事做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 以這個作參考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦戰爭開始的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必定會有傷者出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數百人…數千人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了治療那些傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕對要完成的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人明明說這裡是藥草的寶庫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的難找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要換個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往更高處走走看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得找兵糧丸的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣完全不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 記住味道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個吧…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該是這個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這味道好像不太一樣 又好像有點相似
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪 這種地方的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會生長著曼陀羅草的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是氣候起變化了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是活力人參
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 還是有的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長了一堆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做出很不錯的兵糧丸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敬了 那邊的活力人參是我們先發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個護額 看來是木葉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大國之人是不會在意我們這些小國的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們乃南邊紅州島的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是上忍 阪東
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下忍 佐田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.05,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是木地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳言戰爭臨近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便前來這座小島收集藥草
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 難怪怎麼找都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為你們捷足先登了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 已經收集一大部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.92,0:08:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣一來你們就該苦惱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幫了忍者聯軍的大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.87,0:08:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就…好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算 我算 我算算算…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一束這個價位如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的人真不好商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我好好學習學習…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要收錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是送給我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了小的們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這樣的小國是生存不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 木葉若不願意購買的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就指望其他村裡的大名殿下們出資了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭中會受傷的不只是忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…明知道如此還做買賣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不也是靠任務賺錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.22,0:09:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分出級別 標上價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了…無論如何敬請諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也需要掙回自我防禦的資金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔一株為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔兩株為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔三株為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拔四株為了錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就無法完成任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這樣說 又不能半路搶劫他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然 都組成忍者聯軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和其他村子的忍者發生糾紛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.06,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 沒啥好苦惱的 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座島是藥草的寶庫對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這附近被他們搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒啥了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所說極是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來才是珍稀物品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過不是那麼容易採集到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.52,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有個棘手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼暫且告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.88,0:10:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了藥草為何肚子會疼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藥草
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是誤吃了毒草吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.44,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近應該長著大蔓籐才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被采掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快 再慢點什麼都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蔓籐的花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還留著一些嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 那些傢伙不是給我們留了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下的是為了播種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采草不除根是採藥草的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 不是為了我們留的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去下一個吧 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去河流上游找紅蠑螈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.77,0:12:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.52,0:12:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 寫著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勿過此橋 紅州專用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼不要過橋 我就過給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 肚子也好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體麻痺得動彈不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這捲起的不是麻痺草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個圈套 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那個了…救…救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到紅蠑螈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 紅蠑螈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來就這麼一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這尺寸不過是個娃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能放生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被算計了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪時間被平白無故地浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 怎能這麼悠哉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊去下一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是誰讓我們這麼悠閒的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 只能去這裡了 地獄谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地獄谷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地底湧出的泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能治療撞傷 刀傷 扭傷等等的萬能泥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是綱手大人她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡若有餘力去看看也行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切不可勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是相當危險的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去地獄谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們別老是做偷雞摸狗的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 怎麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能對木葉的各位做那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是做採集藥草的準備罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不跟你們一般見識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到萬能泥漿就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 又想拖住我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無償服務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯會時不時地噴出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是毒氣 長時間接觸的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是無規則的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能得到深處的萬能泥漿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多重影分身之術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.41,0:15:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 萬能泥漿 我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙  沒工具拿不走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:16:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是個大賭博啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能碰運氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧您 總算確認好路線了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做生意可不是抱著玩玩的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了小國的生存 我們也得拚死努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等瓦斯消失後就上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁.大突破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁之術 挺能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁.大突破 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光跑來不及的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風遁.大…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你們幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欠下大國的情 之後不知道要賠多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會要錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一直對我們小國…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說這是無償服務了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大玉螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 該怎麼說呢 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 真的不收錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早說是免費的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是他國的忍者 也不全是敵對的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:18:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.96,0:19:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候也突破利益關係攜手合作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的忍者聯軍就是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.44,0:19:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐田 木地 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真是免費的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著感恩的心來接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是來自我們的免費服務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下這萬能泥漿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊所有已經採集好的藥草也請收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就算我們送給忍者聯軍的禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 任務完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 你才是 今天深受啟發了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 你們也加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣合適嗎 阪東大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免費給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在給聯軍一個恩惠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點小虧就能得到好處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再會了 大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時的離別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我的身體已經能適應船了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 加油啊 特別任務加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被詛咒的幽靈船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在霧中浮現出來的謎一般的蒸汽船
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了進行調查 踏上船的鳴人一行碰到一名少年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又肩負如何悲哀的秘密呢
